li.al:
the term “designated airline" means an airline which has
                been designated and authorized in accordance with Article 3 of
                this Agreement;

the terms “agreed service" and “specified route"
                mean international air service pursuant to Article 2 of this
                Agreement and the route specified in the Annex to this Agreement respectively;

the term “stores" means articles of the readily
                consumable nature for use or sale on board an aircraft during
                flight, including commissary supplies;

the term “Agreement" means this Agreement, its Annex
                drawn up in application thereof, and any amendments to the
                Agreement or to the Annex;

the interest of consumers of air transport products will be
                  protected from any misuse of such information including
                  misleading presentation thereof;
